{
  "id": "adv_event_2402_01_03",
  "title": "冬の北海道と\nいえば",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ymk001.m4a",
      "text": "……ああっ！\nあなた達はもしかして、星見プロの……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah!\nAre you perhaps… from Hoshimi Production…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.4712244034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 5.6778909843
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、確か……初音ミクさん、よね？\nバーチャル・シンガーの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ if I remember correctly… You’re Hatsune Miku-san‚ right?\nThe virtual singer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6778909843,
      "endTime": 11.2739682357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 11.9473021347
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "おお～、前にトリエルがライブで共演した、あの！\nこれはなんという偶然の出会い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh~‚ the one TRINITYAiLE performed with before!\nWhat a coincidence!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9473021347,
      "endTime": 19.113379081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 19.3267122427
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "驚いた……こんな所で再会するなんて\nでも、なんで北海道に？　しかもその格好は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m surprised… To meet you again in a place like this.\nBut why are you in Hokkaido? And what’s with that outfit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3267122427,
      "endTime": 27.7453064123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 27.9519730408
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、知らなかったんですか？\nこの衣装、ミクちゃんの『雪ミク衣装』ですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn’t know‚ {user}-san?\nThis is Miku-chan’s “Snow Miku” outfit!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9519730408,
      "endTime": 34.4314969857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 34.618163538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "ミクちゃんは、冬の北海道の魅力を発信して盛り上げる\nアンバサダーとしても活動しているんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku-chan is active as an ambassador\nto promote the charms of Hokkaido in the winter!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.618163538,
      "endTime": 41.382902860799994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 41.58290267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったの\nというか、愛、詳しいわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see.\nYou seem to know a lot about this‚ Ai…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.58290267,
      "endTime": 45.6445806504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 45.8445806981
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、『雪ミク』は有名なので北海道に行った\nことがある人はみんな知ってると思いますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe‚ “Snow Miku” is famous‚ so I think everyone\nwho has been to Hokkaido knows about her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8445806981,
      "endTime": 52.8043993474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 52.9910658997
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "結構前から、毎年アンバサダーを担当してるんだよね\nさすがに本人に会えるとは思ってなかったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s been the ambassador every year for quite some time now.\nI never thought I’d actually get to meet her‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9910658997,
      "endTime": 60.622993199199996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "おっと意外。葵さんまでご存じとは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ that’s surprising. Even Aoi-san knows about her…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8096599421,
      "endTime": 64.4086394629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 64.6219728154
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁね。音ゲーでミクの曲、結構遊んでるから\nそういう知識は自然と入ってくるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I’ve played a lot of Miku’s songs in rhythm games.\nThat kind of knowledge naturally comes to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6219728154,
      "endTime": 71.69528347670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ymk002.m4a",
      "text": "知ってくれていて、ありがとう\nここだと寒いし、もし良かったら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for knowing.\nIt’s cold here‚ so if you’d like…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333333333,
      "endTime": 78.7000005086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 71.9019501052
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.7947159769
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（ミクのご厚意で俺達は、控え室に通してもらった）\n（お互いの積もる話に、しばらく花を咲かせて――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thanks to Miku’s kindness‚ we were led to a waiting room.）\n（We caught up with each other for a while――）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.8613811177,
      "endTime": 88.7744878453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.4999999999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあミクはここ以外にも\n冬の北海道を盛り上げるため、各地で活動してるのね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So you’re working in other places besides here‚ Miku‚\nto promote Hokkaido in the winter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.9878209116,
      "endTime": 94.92804775260001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.114714591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "北海道中を、端から端まで瞬時に移動可能！\n……なんか、カッコいいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She can move instantly from one end of Hokkaido to the other!\nThat’s… so cool!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.114714591,
      "endTime": 101.6863925618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ymk003.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワのみんなと{user}さんは\nなんで北海道に？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What brings LizNoir and {user}-san\nto Hokkaido?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.7,
      "endTime": 106.61997718810001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8930589996
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.4284087342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "今、ライブツアーの真っ最中なんだ\n今回は北海道での公演でね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re in the middle of a live tour right now.\nThis time‚ we’re performing in Hokkaido.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4284087342,
      "endTime": 111.7284087342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワ初の北海道公演！\nそしてファン待望の、こころのセンター公演！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir’s first Hokkaido concert!\nAnd the concert that fans have been waiting for‚ Kokoro’s center performance!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.9417419912,
      "endTime": 119.7755287649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.2666651406
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "北海道中の雪が溶けるくらいの\nあっついステージになる予定ですっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s going to be a performance so hot\nthat the snow in Hokkaido will melt!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9821952027,
      "endTime": 125.4391795319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.6325127126
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、ミク\nこの子、こういう絡み辛いところがあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry about that‚ Miku.\nThis girl… she’s a little hard to deal with…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.6325127126,
      "endTime": 130.6143946172,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.8143948079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっとちょっとちょっと！\n「絡み辛い」はさすがに酷くないですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ hey‚ hey!\n“Hard to deal with” is a bit harsh‚ don’t you think!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8143948079,
      "endTime": 135.4841906071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ymk004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、大丈夫だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ it’s okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3333333333,
      "endTime": 138.3333106835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.6975240549
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.5163478852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、こころがセンターかどうかはさておき\n後半はまさしくその通りだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ setting aside whether Kokoro is center or not‚\nthe second half of what she said is right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5163478852,
      "endTime": 144.81634788510001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.0296813329
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "僕達は歌で、パフォーマンスで、ファンを熱狂させる\nそのために自分達を磨き上げて、ここに来たんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re here to excite the fans with our singing and our performance.\nThat’s why we’ve been working hard to improve ourselves and come here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.0296813329,
      "endTime": 153.7039670308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ymk005.m4a",
      "text": "北海道のファンのみんなにも喜んでもらえる\n最高のステージに出来そうだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounds like it’ll be a great performance\nthat the Hokkaido fans will love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.7,
      "endTime": 160.0399772644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.9173000972
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.1206432661
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、もちろんです！\nただ、せっかく北海道でのライブなんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ of course!\nBut since it’s a concert in Hokkaido‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.1206432661,
      "endTime": 165.84182227460002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "何かサプライズしたいな、って思ってるんですけど\n内容を決めかねてて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was thinking it would be nice to do something special‚\nbut I’m having trouble deciding what to do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.0418194135,
      "endTime": 171.8345857938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 172.0412522316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "普段はなかなか、本州開催のライブに参加出来ない\n北海道在住のファンに向けた感謝の気持ち……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A way to show our gratitude to the fans who live in Hokkaido\nand can’t usually attend our concerts in Honshu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 172.0412522316,
      "endTime": 179.2225674629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.4292342822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "それを、北海道だからこそのサプライズで返せれば\nもっといいライブに出来るって確信はあるのだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we can return that feeling with a surprise that’s only possible because we’re in Hokkaido‚\nI’m sure we can make it an even better live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.4292342822,
      "endTime": 186.53356558480002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.7268988609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりご当地グルメや名産品じゃないかな\n会場外に出店を並べて、小規模フェスっぽくするとか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it should be something related to local gourmet food or specialties.\nLike setting up stalls outside the venue and making it like a small festival.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.7268988609,
      "endTime": 195.2268986702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.4335654895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
