      "text": "さすがに今から各所に依頼を出して準備ってのは\n間に合わないな……残念だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can’t ask people to prepare now‚ it’s too late… It’s a shame‚ but\nwe’re not going to be able to make it in time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.4335654895,
      "endTime": 201.38549296070002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 201.5788263321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
