      "text": "何をもって「北海道だからこそ」って定義するか……\nまずはそこから固めていかないとですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We need to decide what we mean by “only possible because we’re in Hokkaido”…\nWe have to solidify that first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.5788263321,
      "endTime": 209.1783501625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 209.3650167148
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
