      "text": "北海道にちなんだもので食べ物以外だと、動物？\nキタキツネとか、エゾシマリスとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Something that reminds you of Hokkaido‚ other than food‚ would be animals?\nLike the Ezo red fox‚ or the Hokkaido chipmunk…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.3650167148,
      "endTime": 217.47708040880002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 217.6837470373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
