      "text": "ああでも、可愛い系はこころで間に合ってますね\n小動物要素が大渋滞起こしたら、こころがかすみます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I guess we’re good on the cute factor‚ with Kokoro here.\nIf there are too many small animal elements‚ Kokoro will get overshadowed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.6837470373,
      "endTime": 226.0471253714,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 226.2404586475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
