      "text": "そういうのを自分で言える根性、見上げたものだよね\n嫌いじゃないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I admire your guts to say that about yourself.\nI don’t hate it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.2404586475,
      "endTime": 231.9178118389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ymk006.m4a",
      "text": "あの……\n私がゲスト出演するっていうのは、どうかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um…\nHow about I make a guest appearance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.5333333333,
      "endTime": 238.9203909039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
