      "text": "……え？\nミクが……サプライズゲストとしてってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?\nYou mean… as a surprise guest‚ Miku?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 239.132185936,
      "endTime": 243.4922764778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
