      "text": "確かに、『雪ミク』姿のミクが出演してくれれば\n北海道公演だからこそのサプライズだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Miku appeared in her “Snow Miku” outfit‚\nit would be a surprise that’s only possible because we’re doing a Hokkaido concert.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 249.4535236994,
      "endTime": 257.2718228022,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 257.4784894307
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "けど、それだと一方的なオーダーになっちゃうわね\nフェアじゃないのは、さすがに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But that would be a one-sided request.\nIt wouldn’t be fair…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 257.4784894307,
      "endTime": 263.8588975271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-ymk007.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、私と一緒に冬の北海道を盛り上げてほしい！\nリズノワらしい方法で！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I’d like you to help me promote Hokkaido in the winter!\nIn a way that’s unique to LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 263.5,
      "endTime": 272.1599769592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 264.0655641556
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 271.7432961781
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど……ミクは冬の北海道のアンバサダー\nつまり、その手伝いを……ってことか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Miku is an ambassador for Hokkaido in the winter.\nSo you want us to… help you with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 271.7432961781,
      "endTime": 280.49329598739996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
